625
00:27:54,800 --> 00:27:55,680
It will reduce the swelling.

626
00:27:55,680 --> 00:27:56,640
Where else?

627
00:27:56,640 --> 00:27:57,839
Here too.

628
00:27:59,680 --> 00:28:00,599
Oh, gosh.

629
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:01,559
Mom.

630
00:28:02,800 --> 00:28:04,760
