632
00:28:08,479 --> 00:28:09,239
Mind you.

633
00:28:09,239 --> 00:28:10,640
You're about to die?

634
00:28:10,640 --> 00:28:12,479
No tear and bleeding.

635
00:28:12,479 --> 00:28:13,359
