649
00:28:37,239 --> 00:28:38,920
I might as well die.

650
00:28:39,680 --> 00:28:40,760
You're not burning up.

651
00:28:41,319 --> 00:28:42,479
If you're not feeling well,

652
00:28:42,599 --> 00:28:43,520
I'll bring you to a hospital.

653
