694
00:30:08,040 --> 00:30:09,359
Meimei.

695
00:30:09,359 --> 00:30:11,920
Darling. She is a liar.

696
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:15,880
I am a victim, darling.

697
00:30:16,120 --> 00:30:17,479
I have never done anything

698
