to Vivian.

699
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:19,559
I hung out with her

700
00:30:19,559 --> 00:30:22,239
to make you jealous.

701
00:30:23,160 --> 00:30:24,199
I can swear with all the skins

702
00:30:24,199 --> 00:30:26,120
I purchased in the game

703
