705
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:31,439
We truly did nothing.

706
00:30:31,439 --> 00:30:31,880
Darling.

707
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:33,680
You're the best wife in the world.

708
00:30:33,680 --> 00:30:35,559
