709
00:30:35,559 --> 00:30:36,120
Darling!

710
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:39,359
I'm a victim, darling.

711
00:30:40,920 --> 00:30:41,479
Look.

712
00:30:42,520 --> 00:30:44,479
