720
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:57,120
Fine. Leave.

721
00:30:57,120 --> 00:30:59,239
Leave me alone.

722
00:30:59,559 --> 00:31:01,160
I'll be fine.

723
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:02,559
Once you leave,

724
00:31:02,559 --> 00:31:05,839
- I'll leave this world too.
