729
00:31:18,559 --> 00:31:19,520
Darling.

730
00:31:23,439 --> 00:31:24,640
I'm suffering.

731
00:31:26,120 --> 00:31:27,319
Darling.

732
00:31:27,359 --> 00:31:29,599
All right. Get in the car now.

733
00:31:29,599 --> 00:31:30,239
Behave.

734
00:31:31,280 --> 00:31:32,199
